Aron Pinson : SLS Wealth Management














































Share

share

|





 


Aron Pinson
 



  
 Aron Pinson, CFA
Apinson@SLSWealth.com


   

Mr. Pinson brings nearly a decade of professional financial market experience to SLS Wealth. From the young age of 13, Aron was involved in the equity markets, trading his own accounts and learning all that he can about the complex financial marketplace.
Mr. Pinson has a longstanding passion for investing that predates his professional experience in the business. He is a Chartered Financial Analyst and is a member of the CFA institute.
He began his career at a Full Service boutique firm on Wall Street, where he later became an integral part to the firm’s growth. In 2006 he became one of the firm's Registered Principles and the Firm's Options Principal, filling the role of the Firm's CROP and SROP.
He received his Rabbinical Ordination and holds a Bachelors of Arts in Rabbinical Studies. His professional credentials include series 4, 7, 24, 63, 65 and also a Licensed Life Insurance Agent.
Aron and his wife Shani have been happily married since February 2007 and have three gorgeous boys, Chezzy, Yossi, and Menny. Aron is on the board of his local synagogue and is active in many local and national charitable organizations.









