Gaurav Lall






		 

		Gaurav Lall
Glall@SLSWealth.com


	 

For nearly a decade, clients have sought Mr. Lall’s advice in implementing strategic wealth plans that encompass a well balanced approach to investing. Mr.Lall is committed to establishing trust, respect, and a lasting partnership with clients. As Managing Partner and Co-Founder of SLS Wealth, Mr. Lall provides clients with a sense of comfort, control, empowerment and freedom in their financial lives. He seeks the solutions for clients by focusing on each client’s individual goals, objectives and circumstances. To that end, Mr. Lall offers no pre-packaged solutions or cookie-cutter plans; instead strategic wealth plans are individually tailored to meet exacting client needs.Prior to co-founding SLS Wealth, Mr. Lall served as an Associate at Raymond James Financial and then as one of the top Senior Financial Consultants at a boutique firm on Wall Street.Mr. Lall heads the research and analysis department. With the help of his research team, they analyze and diligently research new investment ideas for the betterment of client portfolios. He has established a reputation of hard work and commitment to his clients in order to ensure a long-term, beneficial relationship. Due to his vast knowledge of global markets, he caters to an array of high net worth clients from around the globe. He is also a member of the firm’s Executive Management and Investment Committees.Mr. Lall graduated from the College of Staten Island, with a Bachelor of Science in Finance and Economics. His professional credentials include his series 7, 63, 65, 79 licenses and is also a Licensed Life Insurance Agent.








