SLS Capital Management, LLC: Private Company Information - Bloomberg









































  





















































































July 21, 2017 12:50 PM ET
Capital Markets

Company Overview of SLS Capital Management, LLC



Snapshot People




Company Overview
SLS Capital Management, LLC is an employee owned hedge fund sponsor. The firm primarily provides its services to corporations. It also manages portfolios for pooled investment vehicles. The firm also manages separate client-focused equity accounts. It invests in the public equity markets of the United States. The firm employs a long/sort equity strategy as a technique to hedge its investments. SLS Capital Management is based in New York City.


37 West 57th StreetFloor 10New York, NY 10019United States



Phone: 212-537-3605








